OL,3,CBiker thanks off-duty paramedic who
OL,4,C'saved his life' after crash
OL,6,FWatch: Jerry Moon reflects on the day
OL,7,Fhe says he almost lost his life.
OL,9,FA motorcyclist from Bath who was
OL,10,Fseriously injured in a crash has paid
OL,11,Ftribute to the off-duty paramedic he
OL,12,Fsays saved his life.
OL,14,FJerry Moon was riding his bike through
OL,15,Fslow-moving traffic when he was hit by
OL,16,Fa car near his home on 20 June. The
OL,17,Fcar turned right into a driveway
OL,18,Fwithout any warning, causing him to
OL,19,Flose control of his bike and crash
OL,20,Finto a wall.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
