OL,3,CBiker thanks off-duty paramedic who
OL,4,C'saved his life' after crash
OL,6,FThe 34-year-old told ITV News he
OL,7,F"started saying goodbyes" to his loved
OL,8,Fones at the scene after the accident,
OL,9,Fbecause he thought his injuries would
OL,10,Fbe fatal.
OL,12,FSouth Western Ambulance Service
OL,13,Fparamedic Louise Price had just
OL,14,Ffinished her shift and was walking
OL,15,Fhome when she saw the crash. She
OL,16,Fcalled her colleagues on 999 and
OL,17,Fprovided urgent medical care to Jerry
OL,18,Fat the scene.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
