OL,3,CBiker thanks off-duty paramedic who
OL,4,C'saved his life' after crash
OL,6,F"When I stepped away from the gate
OL,7,Fpost I felt a little bubble in my
OL,8,Fchest that popped, going down towards
OL,9,Fthe floor I knew I was in big
OL,10,Ftrouble," Jerry said.
OL,12,F"I started saying goodbye to everybody
OL,13,Fand thank you for everything that I
OL,14,Fdid in my lifetime - I really thought
OL,15,FI was going."
OL,17,FJerry spent a week in hospital
OL,18,Freceiving treatment for his injuries
OL,19,Fwhich included a fractured ankle,
OL,20,Fbroken ribs, a lacerated lung,
OL,21,Finternal swelling, and bruising.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
