OL,3,CBiker thanks off-duty paramedic who
OL,4,C'saved his life' after crash
OL,6,FHe also underwent cardiac treatment,
OL,7,Fincluding the fitting of a stent due
OL,8,Fto one of his coronary arteries
OL,9,Fclosing.
OL,11,FJerry and his partner met Louise at
OL,12,FPaulton Ambulance Station in
OL,13,FSeptember, to thank her in person for
OL,14,Fher quick actions.
OL,16,F"Amazingly, she was in one of the cars
OL,17,Fthat I'd passed. It was quite a
OL,18,Fsurreal scene. I wanted to say thank
OL,19,Fyou to her and appreciate the time
OL,20,Fthat she gave off-duty.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
