OL,3,CBiker thanks off-duty paramedic who
OL,4,C'saved his life' after crash
OL,6,F"She didn't need to do what she did.
OL,7,FThe NHS team were terrific to me. If
OL,8,Fthey weren't there, and if they didn't
OL,9,Fdo what they did, I wouldn't be here
OL,10,Fto say thank you.
OL,12,F"Someone was watching me that day.
OL,13,FSomeone was looking down on me for
OL,14,FLouise to be in such a position. And
OL,15,Fthere she is, she pops out of nowhere
OL,16,Fto save me. Right time, right place."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
